<bioghist altrender="history" encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
<head>Historical Note</head>
<p>
The Senate created the Committee in August 2007 to review Sen. Louis DeLuca's actions leading up to his guilty plea on a misdemeanor threatening charge. Sen. DeLuca resigned his office effective November 30, 2007.
</p>
</bioghist>

<scopecontent encodinganalog="520" id="a3">
<head>Scope and Content</head>
<p>
Includes meeting material such as agendas, minutes, transcripts and handouts; procedures; correspondence and responses; and resolutions.
</p>
</scopecontent>



